column2: SELECT u.up_col0 as col0, s.specobjid, s.z, g.oh_p5#, g.lgm_tot_p5#, g.lgm_fib_p5#, g.sfr_tot_p5#, g.sfr_fib_p5#, g.specsfr_tot_p5#, g.specsfr_fib_p5# FROM #upload u  JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id  JOIN SpecObjAll s ON s.specObjID = x.specObjID  JOIN galSpecExtra g ON g.specObjID = x.specObjID ORDER by x.up_id&&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
